---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---

<Layout title="Projects | Ernests Smalikis">
	<Navbar />
	<main class="container mx-auto pt-32 pb-20">
		<section class="section max-w-4xl mx-auto">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-10 text-center">üìê What I Build</h1>
			
			<div class="card p-8 md:p-12 mb-12">
				<p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-8 text-center">
					I focus on lean, high-impact software with a strong backend and security posture. My work spans:
				</p>
				
				<ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-lg">
					<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						<span class="h-px w-8 bg-primary"></span>
						<span>Backend APIs & automation tools</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						<span class="h-px w-8 bg-primary"></span>
						<span>Static and full-stack web apps</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						<span class="h-px w-8 bg-primary"></span>
						<span>AI/ML-powered text processing and OSINT utilities</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						<span class="h-px w-8 bg-primary"></span>
						<span>Privacy-first tools for individuals and small businesses</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						<span class="h-px w-8 bg-primary"></span>
						<span>Real-time systems with low-latency performance requirements</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
				
				<p class="text-lg italic mb-10 text-center text-accent">
					Tools are tested in the wild ‚Äî not just in dev environments.
				</p>
				
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-primary">Featured Projects</h2>
				
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div class="card border-t-4 border-primary">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">XStagePass</h3>
						<p>Event management software with task-based access control, Google Drive image uploads, and real-time updates. Supports both hosted and self-hosted deployments.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="card border-t-4 border-accent">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">LuceneX Insight</h3>
						<p>AI-driven browser tool for extracting and summarizing text while ignoring markup and noise. Designed for OSINT and journalism workflows.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="card border-t-4 border-secondary">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">SpotEye</h3>
						<p>Surveillance optimization tool that tags and prioritizes video events using smart filtering and human-in-the-loop learning.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="card border-t-4 border-primary">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">XHashPass</h3>
						<p>A battle-tested evolution of my first tool ‚Äî Password generator. Lightweight, secure, and built with modern cryptographic standards in mind.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="text-center">
				<a href="/vision" class="button-primary inline-flex items-center gap-3">
					<span>üéØ</span>
					<span>See My Vision</span>
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
